  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA45-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu kuṟai vēṇṭiya (ET: niṉṟa) talaivaṉait tōḻi cēṭpaṭuttatu (ET: cēṭpaṭa uraittatu).</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how the confidante kept HIM who had requests at a distance.</p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="NA45">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            ivaḷē, kāṉa ṉaṇṇiya kāmar ciṟukuṭi</l>
<l>            nīṉiṟap peruṅkaṭal kalaṅka vuḷpukku</l>
<l>            mīṉeṟi paratavar {kātaṉ} makaḷē</l>
<l>            nīyē, neṭuṅkoṭi nuṭaṅku niyama mūtūrk</l>
<l>            kaṭuntērc celvaṉ kātaṉ makaṉē </l>
<l>            niṇaccuṟā vaṟutta vuṇakkal vēṇṭi</l>
<l>            yiṉappu ḷōppu memakkunala ṉevaṉō</l>
<l>            pulavu nāṟutuñ celaniṉ ṟīmō</l>
<l>            perunīr viḷaiyuḷeñ ciṟunal vāḻkkai </l>
<l>            nummoṭu puraivatō vaṉṟē </l>
<l>            yemma ṉōriṟ cemmalu muṭaittē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>She,</l>
<l rend="indent2">she [is] the daughter of fishermen, catching fish,</l>
<l rend="indent3">entering the inside of the blue-coloured great sea so that it is stirred up, </l>
<l rend="indent3">with desirable small homes situated by the seashore grove.</l>
<l>You,</l>
<l rend="indent2">you [are] the beloved son of a wealthy man with quick chariot,</l>
<l rend="indent3">from an old village with a market place,</l>
<l rend="indent3">where long flags are swaying.</l>
<l>What good [is there] to us who are chasing away birds in flocks,</l>
<l rend="indent2">wanting dry pieces cut from the fat shark?</l>
<l>We are smelling of fish. Stay away!<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">cela niṉṟīmō</term>: apart from the unusual imperative, <term xml:lang="ta">nil</term> is clearly employed here as an auxiliary: "going away stay [there]".</note></l>
<l rend="indent2">Our little good living from the produce of the great water</l>
<l>is nothing great with you.</l>
<l>For our likes it possesses all the excellence.</l>
       </lg>
         </div>
